        ("You decide to try again later. What do you say?",["okay","give you space","when ready","talk later","whenever","not rushing","here when","take your time"],"Give them space","Okay I understand I will give you some space and we can talk when you feel ready","nod"),
        ("They come to you later and are calmer. What do you say?",["glad you came","thank you","ready to talk","sorted out","explain","still want","clear up","good you came"],"Welcome them","I am really glad you came back I still want us to clear this up so we can both feel better","wave"),
        ("You explain again calmly. They understand. What do you say?",["glad","see","finally","relieved","good","understand","all makes sense","sorted","cleared","better"],"Express relief","I am so relieved you understand now I really did not want this between us","nod"),
        ("What do you learn from this experience?",["patience","take time","give space","not everyone ready","listen","both sides","important to clarify","communication"],"Reflect","I learned that sometimes people need time before they are ready to hear your side and that patience helps","think"),
