        ("They say they are not sure. What do you suggest?",["how about","we could","want to","maybe","if you want","idea","hang out","suggestion","something fun"],"Make a suggestion","Maybe we could hang out if you are free I have been wanting to catch up in person too","wave"),
        ("They say that sounds great. What do you say?",["yes","perfect","love that","let us plan","cannot wait","great","so glad","will sort","get the details"],"Agree","Brilliant let us sort out the details and make it happen I cannot wait","nod"),
        ("You both go quiet again. How do you feel about the silence this time?",["okay","comfortable","fine","not awkward","good sign","means close","natural","relax"],"Be comfortable","I would feel comfortable with it a brief silence with a good friend is natural and not awkward","nod"),
        ("They say they have to go soon. What do you say?",["okay","no worries","glad we talked","catch up soon","enjoyed","talk later","speak soon","bye for now"],"Acknowledge","Okay no worries I am so glad we had this chat speak soon yeah","nod"),
