        ("You want to say one last thing. What do you say?",["oh one more","quick thing","before you go","just quickly","last thing","almost forgot","by the way","one sec"],"Add a final thought","Oh before you go I just wanted to say it was really lovely catching up I have missed talking to you","nod"),
        ("They say the same. How do you respond?",["me too","same","so good","agree","love our chats","catch up more often","miss you too","glad we called"],"Respond warmly","Me too we should do this more often I always feel better after talking to you","nod"),
        ("You say your final goodbye. What do you say?",["bye","take care","speak soon","talk later","catch you","until next","bye for now","chat soon","see you","take care of yourself"],"Say goodbye","Okay take care speak soon bye for now","wave"),
