        ("They mention they play football. What do you say?",["really","love sport","play too","watch football","which team","how long","that is cool","amazing","sport is great"],"Show interest","That is really cool do you play for a team or just casually what position do you play","think"),
        ("They are enjoying the conversation. What do you notice?",["smiling","engaged","talking lots","relaxed","comfortable","opening up","eye contact","leaning in","enjoying"],"Notice positive signs","I can tell they are enjoying the conversation they are smiling and engaged which makes me feel confident","nod"),
